{"tid":2309046,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2978新入職公務員已聲明效忠特區　警務處消防處教育局最多共789人","createTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T10:22:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e679d0dd084191a49ce2751339010a27defec94a","tid":2309046,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局長聶德權今（2日）在立法會回覆議員提問，表示在今年7月1日至10月31日期間，已聲明擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區的新入職公務員共有2978名，分別來自約140個職系，最多人員已聲明的首3個部門，分別是警務處302人、消防處246人及教育局241人。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局在今年10月12日向各部門發出通告，要求所有在今年7月1日或之後加入香港特區政府的公務員，宣誓或作出聲明擁護《基本法》、效忠香港特區和對香港特區政府負責，作為聘用條件的一部分；直接獲聘至較高級職位（如部門首長）的公務員，則會獲安排進行宣誓。"},{"pid":"e173e51887480acca419a95fbf979d3fbbec4919","tid":2309046,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69KZu85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69KZu85.gif&h=7cd03a04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d02415ccc3d2245e22eca0c16bc858322a37cc6","tid":2309046,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"之前嘅唔鳩駛表明效忠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a4bdd10fe0f8b19efd41cf352bb3dde8acc016","tid":2309046,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d02415ccc3d2245e22eca0c16bc858322a37cc6","tid":2309046,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"之前嘅唔鳩駛表明效忠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"全部在職公務員都要宣誓"},{"pid":"346368eca9c678e066cc3e2d76aae448a3ba9de4","tid":2309046,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a4bdd10fe0f8b19efd41cf352bb3dde8acc016","tid":2309046,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dis